data.description: LOTS of Room for EVERYONE! Spacious 4 Bedroom home w/office or possible 5th bedroom in desirable Heritage Park. NEW exterior paint! Large kitchen features eating bar, Newer SS Appliances, Gas Range, and Oversized pantry. Slider off of kitchen leads to large backyard deck and nicely landscaped/fully fenced backyard. Newer vinyl plank flooring & carpet throughout the house. Large Master Suite with x-large w/walk-in closet, jetted soaker tub, & dual vanities. RV Parking w/parking pad & gate.
